snippet.textDisplay:
Finally, My heartfelt review after 12 years of continuously listening to this song:

  This is one of those rare songs that doesn't let you just play itself in the background of your earphones just to avoid the noise of the crowd but instead grabs you by your collar and makes you submit to it's magnificence. 
   Every notes on the play sheet is dancing all over and how it creates a outstanding composition is beyond comprehension.
    Vishal dadlani, a talented man.Respect.
      
       Every now and then, songs like this emerges and only a nieche group hears it. I guess the taste of the mass got so deranged and idiotic, they skip songs like this just because they cannot comprehend the sheer complexity and beauty of the composition.    I guess they all hear like radio static aah sounds when they hear songs like these😂
   Seriously, people have become dumber. Hell even I'm guilty for liking skibidi toilet .forgive me🙏

But I'm still holding onto my taste for quality. Songs that are allowed to call an art. 
This song is one of them !!!❣️
